Holger Pedersen may refer to:
* Holger Pedersen (linguist), Danish linguist (1867–1953)
* Holger Pedersen (astronomer), Danish astronomer (b. 1946), at the European Southern Observatory
* Holger Petersen, Canadian radio personality
